name: AC_serial_2021-10-11-03-46-2(haru-yozora)-Fragment
description:
A-Mashiro is a commercial photographer and painter in Japan.These works are processed from his photographs and Digital painted by his own hands. These are his works made from everyday landscapes.
This work is a still image of one of the gif images.The meaning of haru-yozora in Japanese is spring-night sky.
